nnoremap <silent> <Tab> >>
vnoremap <silent> <Tab> >gv
nnoremap <silent> <S-Tab> <<
vnoremap <silent> <S-Tab> <gv

"binds to make HL behave like a stronger h and l
nnoremap <silent> H ^
nnoremap <silent> L $
vnoremap <silent> H ^
vnoremap <silent> L $


"Open vimrc in
nnoremap <silent> <leader>ev :e ~/.ideavimrc<cr>

"Use jj instead of escape
imap jj <c-c>

"Some command remaps to not have to pay attention
cnoreabbrev W w
cnoreabbrev Wa wa
cnoreabbrev WA wa
cnoreabbrev Q q
cnoreabbrev Qa qa
cnoreabbrev QA qa

set number
set relativenumber

set surround
